The 'Life Sim' tag on SteamDB lists games that offer immersive and open-ended simulated experiences. These games often allow players to create and manage their own virtual lives, from building relationships and careers to managing households and personal hobbies. Players can explore various aspects of life in a realistic and engaging way, with some games focusing on specific themes such as farming, cooking, or running a business. The 'Life Sim' category caters to those who enjoy the freedom and depth that comes with creating and living in their own virtual world.
